Class Navigator

  • java.lang.Object
    • stacks.Navigator

  • public class Navigator
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides navigation feature. Uses 2 stacks backLinks and forwardLinks to store the history of links navigated by the user

    • Method Detail

      • setCurrentLink

        public void setCurrentLink(java.lang.String link)
        Sets the current link of the navigator to specified link and updates the backLinks and forwardLinks stacks. When a user requests a new link, push the current link on the backLinks stack and clear the forwardLinks stack.
        Parameters:
        link - current requested link
